RESTRICTIONS

You are NOT permitted to:

1. SELL OR REDISTRIBUTE THE GAME — You may not sell, redistribute, or publish
   any product that Substantially Reproduces The Game's Protected Elements,
   whether using The Codebase, Non-Code Assets, or independently recreated
   versions of either.

2. MONETIZE USING NON-CODE ASSETS — You may not Monetize any project that
   incorporates Non-Code Assets from The Game in any form.

3. RELEASE FULL GAME PORTS — You may not publish a standalone, fully or
   substantially playable port of The Game to another language, platform, or
   engine, regardless of whether original or recreated assets are used.

4. OMIT CREDIT — Any publicly released Derivative Work, mod, patch, or port
   must provide clear, visible credit to Cotordo Games (DJ / Djalroid) as the
   original author of The Codebase. This credit must appear:
     a) Within the project itself in a visible location, such as a title
        screen, credits screen, about page, or equivalent; AND
     b) In any public repository description, README, or store/distribution
        page associated with the project.
   Burying credit exclusively in source code comments or obscure documentation
   does not constitute compliance.

5. SUBLICENSE — You may not relicense The Codebase or any Derivative Work
   under different terms that would grant permissions beyond those defined here.

6. CLAIM OWNERSHIP — You may not represent The Codebase, The Game, or any
   substantial portion thereof as your own original work.

